#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Pričetek"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a short introduction to &kmail; and its usage so you can start "
"working with it right away. For more in-depth information see the <link "
"linkend=\"using-kmail\">Using &kmail;</link> section."
msgstr ""
"To je kratek uvod v uporabo &kmail;-a. Z uporabo lahko začnete takoj. Za več "
"podrobnosti si poglej poglavje<link linkend=\"using-kmail\">Uporaba &kmail;-"
"a</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Account Wizard</title>"
msgstr "<title>Čarovnik za račune</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first time you run &kmail; you will be greeted by the Account Wizard."
msgstr "Ob prvem zagonu &kmail;-a, vas bo pozdravil čarovnik za račune."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If at any time you need to run the account wizard again, you can find it "
"under <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Account</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če boste morali kadar koli znova zagnati čarovnika za račune, ga boste našli "
"v razdelku <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj "
"račun</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wizard will lead you through the process of creating an email account. "
"Your screens will vary depending on how much the wizard can determine on its "
"own. Here is an outline of the screens you will encounter while using this "
"wizard."
msgstr ""
"Čarovnik vas bo vodil skozi postopek ustvarjanja e-poštnega računa. Vaši "
"zasloni se razlikujejo glede na to, koliko lahko čarovnik določi sam. V "
"nadaljevanju so opisani zasloni, s katerimi se boste srečali med uporabo "
"tega čarovnika."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:49 getting-started.docbook:77
#: getting-started.docbook:105 getting-started.docbook:133
#: getting-started.docbook:162 getting-started.docbook:187
#: getting-started.docbook:199 getting-started.docbook:228
#: getting-started.docbook:244 getting-started.docbook:275
#: getting-started.docbook:308 getting-started.docbook:325
#: getting-started.docbook:341 getting-started.docbook:357
#: getting-started.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "&nbsp;"
msgstr "&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first screen of the wizard is <guilabel>Provide personal data</"
"guilabel>. It will prompt you for your basic account information: "
"<guilabel>Full name:</guilabel>, <guilabel>E-mail address</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>Password</guilabel>. By default, the <guilabel>Find provider "
"settings on the Internet</guilabel> option is checked, so the wizard will "
"attempt to retrieve the necessary information from the email server. Uncheck "
"this option if you are an expert user and you want to set up an advanced "
"configuration. Click the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> button when finished."
msgstr ""
"Prvo okno čarovnika je <guilabel>Posredujte osebne podatke</guilabel>. "
"Zahteval bo osnovne podatke o računu: <guilabel>Polno ime:</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>E-poštni naslov</guilabel> in <guilabel>Geslo</guilabel>. Privzeto "
"je označena možnost <guilabel>Poišči nastavitve ponudnika na internetu</"
"guilabel>, zato bo čarovnik poskušal pridobiti potrebne informacije iz e-"
"poštnega strežnika. Če ste strokovni uporabnik in želite nastaviti napredne "
"nastavitve, ne označite te možnosti. Ko končate, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Account Wizard</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Čarovnik za račune</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Account Wizard</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Čarovnik za račune</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Provide personal data\" dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno \"Posredujte osebne podatke\""

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"GMail accounts must use &IMAP;. If you have enabled 2-step verification for "
"your GMail account, you will have to get a verification code from Google as "
"part of the initial account setup process. You will not have to perform 2-"
"factor verification after the &kmail; account has been created, because "
"Google marks your &IMAP; link as fully trusted."
msgstr ""
"Računi GMail morajo uporabljati &IMAP;. Če ste v računu GMail omogočili "
"dvostopenjsko preverjanje, boste morali v postopku začetne nastavitve računa "
"od Googla pridobiti kodo za preverjanje. Po ustvarjanju računa &kmail; vam "
"ne bo treba opraviti 2-stopenjskega preverjanja, saj Google vašo povezavo "
"&IMAP; označi kot popolnoma zaupanja vredno."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "The next screen helps you set up encryption keys for your mail."
msgstr "Na naslednjem zaslonu lahko nastavite šifrirne ključe za pošto."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Account Wizard 2</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Čarovnik za račune 2</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:90 getting-started.docbook:121
#: getting-started.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Account Wizard 2</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Čarovnik za račune 2</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "The encryption options dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno možnosti šifriranja"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to secure your communications with GnuPG you can generate a new "
"key and publish the key on a public key server, or you can import an "
"existing key. If you decide to generate a new key pair, do not forget the "
"password used to generate it. You will need that password every time you "
"want to use the key."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zavarovati svoje komunikacije z GnuPG, lahko ustvarite nov ključ "
"in ga objavite na strežniku javnih ključev ali pa uvozite obstoječi ključ. "
"Če se odločite ustvariti nov par ključev, ne pozabite gesla, s katerim ste "
"ga ustvarili. To geslo boste potrebovali vsakič, ko boste želeli uporabiti "
"ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When sending mail, &kmail; optionally looks for encryption keys for your "
"recipients, and encrypts the message if a key can be found. &kmail; can also "
"sign your mail cryptographically, so that each recipient can verify that "
"your message has not been tampered with."
msgstr ""
"Pri pošiljanju pošte &kmail; po želji poišče šifrirne ključe za prejemnike "
"in šifrira sporočilo, če ključ najde. &kmail; lahko pošto tudi kriptografsko "
"podpiše, tako da lahko vsak prejemnik preveri, da vaše sporočilo ni bilo "
"spremenjeno."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <guilabel>Setup complete</guilabel> screen will appear if the wizard "
"determined the account type successfully. Click <guibutton>Details...</"
"guibutton> to view the settings &kmail; has established. Click the "
"<guibutton>Finish</guibutton> button to set up the account, complete the "
"wizard, and close the window."
msgstr ""
"Če je čarovnik uspešno določil vrsto računa, se prikaže zaslon "
"<guilabel>Nastavljanje je zaključeno</guilabel>. Kliknite "
"<guibutton>Podrobnosti...</guibutton>, da si ogledate nastavitve, ki jih je "
"vzpostavil &kmail;. Kliknite gumb <guibutton>Zaključi</guibutton>, da "
"nastavite račun, dokončate čarovnika in zaprete okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account Wizard 3"
msgstr "Čarovnik za račune 3"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "The account type selection dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za izbiro vrste računa"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the wizard cannot determine your account type, the <guilabel>Select "
"Account Type</guilabel> screen will appear. Select your account type from "
"the list (if you do not know, you will need to contact your email provider). "
"If your account type is not listed, click the <guibutton>Check for more on "
"Internet</guibutton> button. Once your account type has been selected, click "
"the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> button, and you will be presented with the "
"<guilabel>Personal Settings</guilabel> screen."
msgstr ""
"Če čarovnik ne more določiti vaše vrste računa, se prikaže zaslon "
"<guilabel>Izberite vrsto računa</guilabel>. S seznama izberite svojo vrsto "
"računa (če je ne poznate, se obrnite na ponudnika e-pošte). Če vaša vrsta "
"računa ni navedena, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Za dodatne preveri na "
"internetu</guibutton>. Ko izberete vrsto računa, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Naprej</guibutton> in prikazalo se bo okno <guilabel>Osebne "
"nastavitve</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the wizard could not locate your email server by searching the internet, "
"the <guibutton>Personal Settings</guibutton> screen will appear."
msgstr ""
"Če čarovnik z iskanjem po internetu ni mogel najti vašega e-poštnega "
"strežnika, se prikaže zaslon <guibutton>Osebne nastavitve</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account Wizard 4"
msgstr "Čarovnik za račune 4"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Personal Settings\" dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno \"Osebne nastavitve\""

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be certain to enter all this information correctly. Select "
"<guilabel>Download all messages for offline use</guilabel> if you want your "
"messages to be accessible when you do not have an Internet connection "
"(&IMAP; only). Click the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> button when finished. "
"The <guilabel>Setup complete</guilabel> screen will appear."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da ste vse te podatke vnesli pravilno. Izberite "
"<guilabel>Prejmi vsa sporočila za uporabo brez povezave</guilabel>, če "
"želite, da so vaša sporočila dostopna, ko nimate internetne povezave (samo "
"&IMAP;). Ko končate, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>. Prikaže se "
"zaslon <guilabel>Nastavljanje je zaključeno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your account has now been set up, and you can click the <guibutton>Finish</"
"guibutton> button to complete the wizard and close the window, or click the "
"<guibutton>Details...</guibutton> button to review the account settings."
msgstr ""
"Vaš račun je zdaj nastavljen in lahko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Končaj</"
"guibutton> za dokončanje čarovnika in zaprtje okna ali kliknete gumb "
"<guibutton>Podrobnosti...</guibutton> za pregled nastavitev računa."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish to create an account manually, please continue reading this "
"chapter. Otherwise, you may safely skip ahead to <link linkend=\"testing-"
"your-setup\">Testing your Setup</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite račun ustvariti ročno, nadaljujte z branjem tega poglavja. V "
"nasprotnem primeru lahko mirno preskočite na <link linkend=\"testing-your-"
"setup\">Preverjanje vaših nastavitev</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manual Configuration Quickstart"
msgstr "Hitri začetek ročnega nastavljanja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The configuration screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zaslon z nastavitvami</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The configuration screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zaslon z nastavitvami</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail;'s main configuration screen"
msgstr "&kmail;-ov glavni zaslon z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Configure &kmail;...</guisubmenu></menuchoice> window "
"consists of six sections: <guilabel>Accounts</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Appearance</guilabel>, <guilabel>Composer</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Security</guilabel>, <guilabel>Misc</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>Plugins</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Okno <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Configure &kmail;...</guisubmenu></menuchoice> sestavlja 6 "
"odsekov: <guilabel>Računi</guilabel>, <guilabel>Videz</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel>, <guilabel>Varnost</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Razno</guilabel>, in <guilabel>Vtičniki</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To begin sending and receiving messages you will only have to change some "
"settings on the <guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> page. Here is a brief synopsis "
"of the steps you must take to set up a new mail account. For a more detailed "
"description, please read the <link linkend=\"configure-generalinfo\"> "
"Configure &kmail;</link> chapter."
msgstr ""
"Če želite začeti pošiljati in prejemati sporočila, morate spremeniti le "
"nekaj nastavitev na strani <guilabel>Računi</guilabel>. Tukaj je kratek "
"povzetek korakov, ki jih morate opraviti za vzpostavitev novega poštnega "
"računa. Za podrobnejši opis preberite poglavje <link linkend=\"configure-"
"generalinfo\">Nastavi &kmail;</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting your Identity"
msgstr "Nastavljanje identitete"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new identity, click the <guilabel>Add...</guilabel> button on "
"the <guilabel>Identities</guilabel> tab associated with the "
"<guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> page. A small pop-up window will appear."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo identiteto, kliknite gumb <guilabel>Dodaj...</"
"guilabel> na zavihku <guilabel>Identitete</guilabel>, ki je povezan s "
"stranjo <guilabel>Računi</guilabel>. Pojavilo se bo majhno pojavno okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The new identity dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za novo identiteto</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The new identity dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za novo identiteto</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a new identity"
msgstr "Dodajanje nove identitete"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You have some options here. Give the new identity a name, and select one of "
"the available choices (\"With empty fields\" or \"Use System Settings values"
"\"). Then click <guilabel>OK</guilabel>. The identity configuration screen "
"will appear."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo imate nekaj možnosti. Novo identiteto poimenujte in izberite eno od "
"razpoložljivih možnosti (\"S praznimi polji\" ali \"Uporabi vrednosti "
"sistemskih nastavitev\"). Nato kliknite <guilabel>OK</guilabel>. Prikaže se "
"zaslon za nastavitev identitete."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The new identity dialog continues</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za novo identiteto se nadaljuje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The new identity dialog continues</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za novo identiteto se nadaljuje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring the new identity"
msgstr "Nastavljanje nove identitete"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings in the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab are fairly "
"straightforward. Fill in the <guilabel>Your name</guilabel> field with your "
"full name (&eg;, <userinput>John Doe</userinput>) and the "
"<guilabel>Organization</guilabel> field (optional) with the appropriate "
"information. Next, fill in the <guilabel>Email address</guilabel> field with "
"your email address (&eg; <userinput>john@example.net</userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve razdelka <guilabel>Identiteta</guilabel> so zelo neposredne. V "
"polje <guilabel>Ime</guilabel> vpišite svoje ime (&eg; <userinput>Janez "
"Novak</userinput>), v polje <guilabel>Organizacija</guilabel> pa "
"organizacijo, kateri pripadate (to polje lahko pustite tudi prazno) Sedaj "
"izpolni polje <guilabel>E-naslov</guilabel> s svojim e-naslovom (&eg; "
"<userinput>janez@primer.net</userinput>)."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using <application>PGP</application> or <application>GnuPG</"
"application> you can set your &openpgp; keys and/or &smime; certificates in "
"the <link linkend=\"configure-identity-cryptography"
"\"><guilabel>Cryptography</guilabel></link> tab."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate <application>PGP</application> ali <application>GnuPG</"
"application>, lahko nastavite ključe &openpgp; in/ali potrdila &smime; v "
"zavihku <link linkend=\"configure-identity-cryptography"
"\"><guilabel>Kriptografija</guilabel></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> and <guilabel>Templates</guilabel> tabs "
"can be used to tailor the way outgoing messages from this identity will be "
"formatted and processed. See <link linkend=\"configure-generalinfo"
"\">Configure &kmail;</link> for more detailed instructions."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> in zavihek <guilabel>Predloge</"
"guilabel> lahko uporabite za prilagoditev načina oblikovanja in obdelave "
"izhodnih sporočil iz te identitete. Za podrobnejša navodila glejte <link "
"linkend=\"configure-generalinfo\">Nastavitve &kmail;-a</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optionally, go to the <guilabel>Signature</guilabel> tab and enter your "
"signature. This is a short bit of verbiage that will be automatically "
"appended to all your messages. It has nothing to do with <emphasis>digital "
"signatures</emphasis>. You may also wish to insert a small personal avatar "
"in outgoing message headers via the <guilabel>Picture</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Po želji preidite na zavihek <guilabel>Podpis</guilabel> in vnesite svoj "
"podpis. To je kratek besedni zvezek, ki bo samodejno dodan vsem vašim "
"sporočilom. To nima nič opraviti z <emphasis>digitalnimi podpisi</emphasis>. "
"Morda boste želeli vstaviti tudi majhen osebni avatar v naslove odhodnih "
"sporočil prek zavihka <guilabel>Slika</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting up your Account"
msgstr "Nastavljanje računa"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> page also contains the settings that tell "
"&kmail; how to send and receive your email messages. Many of these settings "
"can vary greatly depending on the way your system is set up, and on the kind "
"of network in which your mail server is located. If you do not know what "
"setting to choose or what to put in a field, consult your <acronym>ISP</"
"acronym> (Internet Service Provider) or system administrator."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek <guilabel>Računi</guilabel> vsebuje nastavitve, ki &kmail;-u "
"povedo, kako naj prejema in pošilja tvojo e-pošto. Večina nastavitev je "
"odvisna od nastavitev vašega računalnika ter omrežja, kjer je poštni "
"strežnik nameščen. Če potrebnih podatkov ne poznaš, se obrni na svojega "
"Ponudnika Internetnih Storitev (<acronym>ISP</acronym>, Internet Service "
"Provider) oz. sistemskega administratorja."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sending Messages"
msgstr "Pošiljanje sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's one way to create an outgoing mail account."
msgstr "Tukaj je en način, kako ustvariti račun za pošiljanje e-pošte."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Outgoing account choices</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Možnosti računa za pošiljanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Outgoing account choices</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Možnosti računa za pošiljanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing an outgoing email account type"
msgstr "Izbira vrste računa za pošiljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button on the "
"<guilabel>Sending</guilabel> tab, this screen will appear. If your computer "
"is connected directly to the internet you will most likely want to choose "
"&SMTP;. If you need to use &Sendmail; or &Microsoft; <acronym>EWS</acronym>, "
"please consult the <link linkend=\"configure-accounts-sending"
"\">Configuration</link> chapter. Whichever type of outgoing account you "
"select, check the box labeled \"Make this the default outgoing account\". "
"(You can easily change this later if you have more than one email account.)"
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Dodaj...</guibutton>se na zavihku "
"<guilabel>Pošiljanje</guilabel>, prikaže ta zaslon. Če je računalnik "
"neposredno povezan z internetom, boste najverjetneje želeli izbrati možnost "
"&SMTP;. Če morate uporabiti &Sendmail; ali &Microsoft; <acronym>EWS</"
"acronym>, si oglejte poglavje <link linkend=\"configure-accounts-sending"
"\">Nastavljanje</link>. Ne glede na to, katero vrsto odhodnega računa "
"izberete, potrdite polje z oznako \"Nastavi tega kot privzeti račun za "
"pošiljanje\". (Če imate več e-poštnih računov, lahko to pozneje preprosto "
"spremenite.)"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select the <guilabel>&SMTP;</guilabel> option and click the "
"<guibutton>✓ Create and Configure</guibutton> button, the following "
"configuration screen will appear."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete možnost <guilabel>&SMTP;</guilabel> in kliknete gumb "
"<guibutton>✓ Ustvari in nastavi</guibutton>, se prikaže naslednje okno za "
"nastavljanje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The sending configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavitveno pogovorno okno za pošiljanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The sending configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavitveno pogovorno okno za pošiljanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring an &SMTP; account"
msgstr "Nastavljanje &SMTP; računa"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At a minimum, you must supply an email server &URI;. If your email service "
"requires authentication before sending messages, check the \"Server requires "
"authentication\" box and supply your email address and password. If you want "
"&kmail; to remember your password, check the \"Store SMTP password\" box. If "
"you have not yet created a wallet, you will be asked to provide a password."
msgstr ""
"Navesti morate vsaj e-poštni strežnik &URI;. Če vaša e-poštna storitev "
"zahteva preverjanje pristnosti pred pošiljanjem sporočil, potrdite polje "
"\"Strežnik zahteva preverjanje pristnosti\" ter navedite svoj e-poštni "
"naslov in geslo. Če želite, da si &kmail; zapomni vaše geslo, potrdite polje "
"\"Shrani geslo SMTP\". Če si še niste ustvarili denarnice, boste morali "
"navesti geslo."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Verify that the connection to the SMTP server is working by choosing the "
"<guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab and clicking the <guibutton>Auto Detect</"
"guibutton> button. &kmail; will query your &SMTP; server for the correct "
"settings (encryption, port number, and authentication method). After the "
"proper settings have been detected, the outgoing account is ready to use. "
"(Please refer to <link linkend=\"configure-accounts-sending\">Configuration</"
"link> if the &SMTP; connection requires additional fine tuning.)"
msgstr ""
"Preverite, ali povezava s strežnikom SMTP deluje, tako da izberete zavihek "
"<guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> in kliknete gumb <guibutton>Samodejno zaznaj</"
"guibutton>. &kmail; bo poizvedoval po strežniku &SMTP; za pravilne "
"nastavitve (šifriranje, številka vrat in način avtentikacije). Ko so zaznane "
"ustrezne nastavitve, je odhodni račun pripravljen za uporabo. (Če je za "
"povezavo &SMTP; potrebna dodatna natančna nastavitev, glejte <link linkend="
"\"configure-accounts-sending\">Nastavljanje</link>.)"

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Receiving Messages"
msgstr "Prejemanje sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default the <guilabel>Local Folders</guilabel> (inbox, outbox, sent-mail, "
"trash, drafts, and templates) in the primary &kmail; folder are predefined "
"on this tab. Using the drop down box you can set the <guilabel>Retrieval "
"Options</guilabel> for these folders. (Note that &kmail; uses the Maildir "
"format to store messages on your hard disk: each message is stored as a "
"separate file. The exact location of the primary &kmail; directory depends "
"on the &Linux; distribution you have installed, but it is probably in ~/."
"local/share/ somewhere.)"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so na tem zavihku vnaprej določene <guilabel>Mestne mape</guilabel> "
"(prejeto, odposlano, poslana pošta, koš, osnutki in predloge) v primarni "
"mapi &kmail;. V spustnem oknu lahko za te mape nastavite <guilabel>Možnosti "
"pridobivanja</guilabel>. (Upoštevajte, da &kmail; za shranjevanje sporočil "
"na trdem disku uporablja format Maildir: vsako sporočilo je shranjeno kot "
"ločena datoteka. Natančna lokacija primarnega imenika &kmail; je odvisna od "
"distribucije &Linux;, ki ste jo namestili, vendar je verjetno nekje v ~/."
"local/share/.)"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set up an account so you can receive mail, press the <guibutton>Add...</"
"guibutton> button on the <guilabel>Receiving</guilabel> tab. Choose \"Custom "
"Account...\" from the drop down list. You will then be prompted for the "
"account type. Most users will select <guilabel>POP3 E-Mail Server</guilabel> "
"or <guilabel>IMAP E-Mail Server</guilabel>. If you want to use a local "
"mailbox file (<guilabel>Mbox</guilabel>), please see the <link linkend=\"faq-"
"file-locking\">FAQ about file locking</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti račun, da boste lahko prejemali pošto, pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Dodaj...</guibutton> na zavihku <guilabel>Prejemanje</guilabel>. "
"Izberite \"Račun po meri...\" s spustnega seznama. Nato boste pozvani k "
"izbiri vrste računa. Večina uporabnikov bo izbrala možnost <guilabel>E-"
"poštni strežnik POP3</guilabel> ali <guilabel>E-poštni strežnik IMAP</"
"guilabel>. Če želite uporabiti datoteko lokalnega poštnega predala "
"(<guilabel>Mbox</guilabel>), glejte <link linkend=\"faq-file-locking"
"\">Pogosta vprašanja o zaklepanju datotek</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The receiving configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavitveno pogovorno okno za prejemanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The receiving configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavitveno pogovorno okno za prejemanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring an &IMAP; account"
msgstr "Nastavljanje &IMAP; računa"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you chose &POP3; or &IMAP;, the account settings window will appear. "
"First, fill in the <guilabel>Account Name</guilabel> field to name your "
"account. You can choose any name you like. <guilabel>Username</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Password</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Incoming mail server</guilabel> "
"(or <guilabel>IMAP Server</guilabel>) should be filled in with the "
"appropriate information from your <acronym>ISP</acronym> or system "
"administrator. If you want &kmail; to check for new messages automatically, "
"check the <guilabel>Enable interval mail checking</guilabel> box and set the "
"time interval you desire."
msgstr ""
"Če ste izbrali možnost &POP3; ali &IMAP;, se prikaže okno z nastavitvami "
"računa. Najprej izpolnite polje <guilabel>Ime računa</guilabel> in "
"poimenujte svoj račun. Izberete lahko poljubno ime. <guilabel>Uporabniško "
"ime</guilabel>, <guilabel>Geslo</guilabel> in <guilabel>Strežnik prejemanja "
"pošte</guilabel> (ali <guilabel>strežnik IMAP</guilabel>) morajo biti "
"izpolnjeni z ustreznimi informacijami vašega <acronym>ISP</acronym> "
"(ponudnik internetnih storitev ali sistemskega skrbnika. Če želite, da "
"&kmail; samodejno preverja nova sporočila, potrdite polje <guilabel>Vključi "
"intervalno preverjanje pošte</guilabel> in nastavite želeni časovni interval."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, click on the <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab and then the "
"<guibutton>Auto Detect</guibutton> button. &kmail; will query your incoming "
"message server to determine the correct settings for this account "
"(encryption, port number, and authentication method)."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite zavihek <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> in nato gumb "
"<guibutton>Samodejno zaznaj</guibutton>. &kmail; bo poizvedoval po strežniku "
"za dohodna sporočila in določil pravilne nastavitve za ta račun (šifriranje, "
"številka vrat in način overjanja)."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options only relevant to IMAP"
msgstr "Z IMAP povezane možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check <guilabel>Automatically compact folders</guilabel> on the "
"<guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> configuration tab, &kmail; removes the "
"messages you deleted from the server as soon as you leave that folder. "
"Otherwise, the messages are only marked as deleted and it is up to you to "
"compact the folders manually."
msgstr ""
"Če obkljukaš <guilabel>Avtomatsko zavrzi zbrisana sporočila</guilabel> bo "
"&kmail; ob spremembi mape sporočila, določena za izbris tudi dejansko "
"zbrisal iz strežnika. V nasprotnem primeru so sporočila zgolj označena za "
"brisanje in so fizično zbrisana ob ukazu <guimenuitem>Stisnemo vse mape</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options only relevant to POP3"
msgstr "S POP3-jem povezane možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Leave fetched messages on the server</guilabel> on the "
"<guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> configuration tab if you want to leave your "
"messages on the server after you have downloaded them. There are seven ways "
"to specify how long old messages will be kept after being downloaded: "
"indefinitely (leave all options unselected), or number of days / number of "
"messages / maximum size of server side inbox (choose one, two, or all "
"three). If this box is not checked, all messages will be immediately deleted "
"from the remote server after downloading is complete."
msgstr ""
"Če želite sporočila po prenosu pustiti na strežniku, izberite "
"<guilabel>Pustiti pridobljena sporočila na strežniku</guilabel> na "
"nastvitvenem zavihku <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel>. Na voljo je sedem "
"načinov za določitev, kako dolgo se bodo stara sporočila hranila po prenosu: "
"za nedoločen čas (ne izberite nobene možnosti) ali število dni / število "
"sporočil / največja velikost poštnega predala na strani strežnika (izberite "
"eno, dve ali vse tri možnosti). Če to polje ni označeno, bodo vsa sporočila "
"po končanem prenosu takoj izbrisana iz oddaljenega strežnika."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab you can also select <guilabel>Use "
"pipelining for faster mail download</guilabel> if this is supported by your "
"server. Test this to make sure it works safely."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> lahko izberete tudi možnost "
"<guilabel>Uporabi cevljenje za hitrejše prejemanje pošte</guilabel>, če to "
"podpira vaš strežnik. Preizkusite, ali deluje varno."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>inbox</guilabel> is the default folder for incoming messages. "
"If you want to change that for some reason, you can do so with "
"<guilabel>Destination folder</guilabel>. But what you probably want is a "
"<link linkend=\"filters\">filter</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prejeto</guilabel> je privzeta mapa za prihajajočo pošto. Če bi to "
"radi iz katerega koli razloga spremenili, to lahko naredite preko ukaza "
"<guilabel>Ciljna mapa</guilabel>. Verjetneje pa je, da želite uporabiti "
"<link linkend=\"filters\">filter</link>, ki s to možnostjo nima nič skupnega."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With <guilabel>Pre-command</guilabel> you can specify a program that &kmail; "
"should execute before fetching mail. Please specify the full path (do not "
"use <quote>~</quote>) and note that &kmail; will not continue until the "
"program returns."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo <guilabel>Predukaza</guilabel> lahko določite program, ki se bo "
"izvedel pred jemanjem pošte. Prosim navedite polno pot in pomnite, da "
"&kmail; ne bo nadaljeval z jemanjem pošte dokler se program ne bo končal."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options for both IMAP and POP3"
msgstr "Možnosti za tako IMAP kot POP3"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>Receiving</guilabel> tab, under <guilabel>Retrieval "
"Options</guilabel>, select <guilabel>Include in Manual Mail Check</guilabel> "
"if you want to check this account whenever you invoke "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Check Mail</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. If you do not select this option you can still check for new "
"messages on this account with <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Check Mail In &gt; </guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku <guilabel>Prejemanje</guilabel> pod <guilabel>Možnosti "
"pridobivanja</guilabel> izberite <guilabel>Vključi v ročno preverjanje "
"pošte</guilabel>, če želite preveriti ta račun vsakič, ko ga prikličete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preveri pošto</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če ne izberete te možnosti, lahko še vedno "
"preverite, ali so nova sporočila v tem računu z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preveri pošto &gt; </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; supports encryption via <guilabel>SSL/TLS</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>STARTTLS</guilabel> (<guilabel>SSL/TLS</guilabel> should be "
"preferred if it is available)."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; podpira šifriranje prek <guilabel>SSL/TLS</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>STARTTLS</guilabel> (prednostno je potrebno izbrati<guilabel>SSL/"
"TLS</guilabel>, če je na voljo)."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail; supports nine authentication methods:"
msgstr "&kmail; podpira devet metod overitve:"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Clear text</guilabel>,"
msgstr "<guilabel>jasno besedilo(Clear text)</guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>PLAIN</guilabel>,"
msgstr "<guilabel>PREPROSTO</guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>LOGIN</guilabel>,"
msgstr "<guilabel>PRIJAVA</guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>CRAM-MD5</guilabel> (recommended if <guilabel>DIGEST-MD5</"
"guilabel> is not available),"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>CRAM-MD5</guilabel> (priporočljivo, kadar <guilabel>DIGEST-MD5</"
"guilabel> ni na voljo),"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>DIGEST-MD5</guilabel> (recommended),"
msgstr "<guilabel>DIGEST-MD5</guilabel> (priporočeno),"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>NTLM</guilabel>,"
msgstr "<guilabel>NTLM</guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>GSSAPINTLM</guilabel>,"
msgstr "<guilabel>GSSAPINTLM</guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>APOP (aka Anonymous)</guilabel>, and"
msgstr "<guilabel>APOP (aka Anonimno)</guilabel>, in"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Gmail</guilabel>."
msgstr "<guilabel>Gmail</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>DIGEST-MD5</guilabel>, <guilabel>CRAM-MD5</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>APOP</guilabel> are secure on their own. The other options are "
"only secure when used together with <guilabel>SSL</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>TLS</guilabel>. You should only use <guilabel>Clear text</"
"guilabel> if your server does not support any of the other authentication "
"methods. <guilabel>Anonymous</guilabel> is supported on &IMAP;, but "
"<guilabel>APOP</guilabel> is not. <guilabel>Gmail</guilabel> authentication "
"is only available for &IMAP; accounts using Google's GMail service."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>DIGEST-MD5</guilabel>, <guilabel>CRAM-MD5</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>APOP</guilabel> so sami po sebi varni. Druge možnosti so varne le, "
"če se uporabljajo skupaj s <guilabel>SSL</guilabel> ali <guilabel>TLS</"
"guilabel>. <guilabel>Jasno besedilo</guilabel> lahko uporabite le, če "
"strežnik ne podpira nobenega od drugih načinov overitve. <guilabel>Anonimno</"
"guilabel> je podprto v &IMAP;, <guilabel>APOP</guilabel> pa ne. "
"<guilabel>Gmail</guilabel> avtentikacija je na voljo le za račune &IMAP;, ki "
"uporabljajo storitev GMail podjetja Google."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Auto Detect</guibutton> button on the <guilabel>Advanced</"
"guilabel> tab to automatically select the most secure settings supported by "
"your server."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>Samodejno zaznaj</guibutton> na zavihku "
"<guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> lahko samodejno izberete najbolj varne "
"nastavitve, ki jih podpira vaš strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You are now ready to receive mail. For &IMAP;, just open your folders in the "
"folder tree in &kmail;'s main window. &kmail; then connects to your server "
"and displays the messages it finds. For POP3 use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Check Mail</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Sedaj lahko prejemate e-pošto. Za &IMAP; odprite mape v drevesunem prikazu "
"map v glavnem oknu programa &kmail;. &kmail; se nato poveže s strežnikom in "
"prikaže najdena sporočila. Za POP3 uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Preveri pošto</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Testing your Setup"
msgstr "Preizkus Nastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, you should send yourself a message to test your configuration. To "
"send a message, either hit <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</"
"keycap></keycombo>, select the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-message-"
"new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>&nbsp;New</"
"guiicon> button, or select the <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New Message...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. "
"The <link linkend=\"the-composer-window\">composer window</link> will "
"appear. Fill in the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> field with your email address "
"and type something in the <guilabel>Subject</guilabel> field. Send the "
"message by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send "
"Mail</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Najprej si pošljite sporočilo, da preizkusite svoje nastavitve. Če želite "
"poslati sporočilo, pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</"
"keycap></keycombo>, izberite gumb "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-message-"
"new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>&nbsp; Novo </"
"guiicon> ali izberite menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo sporočilo...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Pojavi se "
"<link linkend=\"the-composer-window\">okno skladatelja</link>. V polje "
"<guilabel>Za:</guilabel> vpišite svoj e-poštni naslov, v polje "
"<guilabel>Zadeva</guilabel> pa vnesite karkoli. Sporočilo pošljite tako, da "
"izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji pošto</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To check your email, select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Check Mail</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. In the lower "
"right corner of the main window, a progress bar will indicate how many "
"messages are being downloaded. If you receive the message you just sent, "
"then congratulations! If, however, you receive any error messages while "
"testing your setup, make sure that your network connection is working and "
"recheck your settings at <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preveriti e-pošto, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>preveri pošto</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. V spodnjem "
"desnem kotu glavnega okna je v vrstici napredka prikazano, koliko sporočil "
"se prenaša. Če prejmete sporočilo, ki ste ga pravkar poslali, vam čestitamo! "
"Če pa med preizkušanjem nastavitve prejmete sporočila o napakah, se "
"prepričajte, da omrežna povezava deluje, in ponovno preverite nastavitve v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nastavljanje "
"&kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

